entries.title: German detective issues Madeleine McCann update after bombshell claims that suspect Christian Brueckner 'had confessed to abducting girl from Algarve flat'
entries.summary: Convicted paedophile and rapist Christian Brueckner is the man who German investigators believe abducted and killed Madeleine, then aged just three, in Portugal in 2007.
